c: 5
v: 93
t: "Babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza,nta cyaha kuri bogituruka ku byo bariye (mbere y’uko biziririzwa) igihe cyosebatinya Allah (birinda ibyo yabaziririje bamaze kubimenya), bakemera (ko biziririjwe), bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; hanyuma bakarushaho gutinya Allah ndetse bakanamwemera, nanonebakongera gutinya Allah kurushaho bakanakora ibikorwa byiza. Kandi Allah akunda abakora ibikorwa byiza"